	   <tr><td colspan=2>Level 1-4 Newbie Area What ever cons blue/white to you<br><br>4-8 Find a port to Steamfont mountains and get to the kobold camp near there <br><br>8-12 Follow or ask directions to the Gears/Ruins near the minatour caves in steamfont<br><br>12-16 Find a port to Sro and run to the Oasis of marr and kill the caimans and crocs you can try out some DW camians at around 14 and FM<br><br>16-20 go to lake rathe tear and kill the white aviak guards there they are YELLOW/RED<br><br>20-29 you can either stay and hunt the teash mass gnolls in South Karana or head to the lake of ill omen<br><br>29-34/35 go to ocean of tears on the sister island and walk around it till you hit a dwarf spawn with a tent kill the dwarf outside of the tent the one inside will not do a thing even if you kill the other right infront of him later on you can go ahead and kill the 2 dwarves on the otherside<br><br>34/35-40 go to the east waste lands and look for the orc fort go inside invis and circle the place untill you reach a little room with a crystal ball click on the ball and itll bring you to crystal caverns once you go far enough there will be a place with a big hole go down there with lev or take the long walk invis once you reach the bottom enter the onlt room and go right look for the coldian city once there look for a way down to a broken bridge with 4 stalag terros in corners kill them<br><br>40-44/48 go to lavastorm and go to Solb kill kobolds in a group and solo the one at the entrance untill you do<br><br>44/48-51 go back to the Lake of ill omen and stack up a few waterstones and kill the bloodgill underwater there loc is maybe 78 neg 347<br><br>51-55 go back to oot and kill off the seaphury cyclops solo<br>--------------------------------------------------<br>Group every time you get your new spells for a while befor you start soloing again<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
