	   <tr><td colspan=2>No actually this isn't the best way to get to 55. Not only that but killing seafuries gets boring very quick becuase they take so long to die, and Oasis sucks a LOT. <br><br>The most fun way to level is by grouping. Not always the best way since it can take a while to look for a group, but definately the most fun way. Grouping is better exp. than soloing sometime too.<br><br>SolB is not the best spot, for 40-48, especially for magicians who don't get any decent magic based direct damage spells until 44, until which time they are stuck with fire ones, which are useless in Solusek.<br><br>Former EQ Addict.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
